      • onFling

        public boolean onFling(android.view.MotionEvent event1,
                       android.view.MotionEvent event2,
                       float velocityX,
                       float velocityY)
        Description copied from interface: android.view.GestureDetector.OnGestureListener
        Notified of a fling event when it occurs with the initial on down MotionEvent and the matching up MotionEvent. The calculated velocity is supplied along the x and y axis in pixels per second.
        Specified by:
        onFling in interface android.view.GestureDetector.OnGestureListener
        Parameters:
